  <span>Commemorating Dr. Gudmundur "Bo" Bodvarsson (1951-2006), a Leader of the Deep Unsaturated Flow and Transport Investigations</span>
  <i>WATER</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Tsang, C., Lippmann, M., Dobson, P., Tsang, Y., Faybishenko, B., Benson, S., Birkholzer, J., Finsterle, S., Hawkes, D., Hubbard, S., Kneafsey, T., Liu, H., Oldenburg, C. M., Pruess, K., Sonnenthal, E., Villavert, M., Wang, J., Wu, Y., Zimmerman, R. W.</span>

