</span></cite>
    <div class="detail">
      <p class="doi">
    <span>View details for <a href="/https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.ijggc.2012.06.009">DOI 10.1016/j.ijggc.2012.06.009</a></span>
  </p>
  <p class="wos">
    <span>View details for <a href="/https://ws.isiknowledge.com/cps/openurl/service?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_id=info:ut/000316834700028">Web of Science ID 000316834700028</a></span>
