  <span>Separation and capture of CO2 from large stationary sources and sequestration in geological formations.</span>
  <i>Journal of the Air &amp; Waste Management Association </i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Chow, J. C., Watson, J. G., Herzog, A., Benson, S. M., Hidy, G. M., Gunter, W. D., Penkala, S. J., White, C. M.</span>

<span class="details">
   <span class="year">2003</span>; <span class="volume">53 (10)</span><span class="pages">: 1172-1182</span>
</span></cite>
    <div class="detail">
